-- Osmond's Horizon Says It's Holding Acquisition Talks With Crest Nicholson
-- James Cone
-- 2010-04-26T06:06:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-26/osmond-s-horizon-says-it-s-holding-acquisition-talks-with-crest-nicholson.html

          
          
             Horizon Acquisition Co. Plc said it
is in preliminary discussions with several companies, including
Crest Nicholson, with a view to a potential transaction. Horizon
said “no view can be expressed” as to whether a transaction
will result from the talks.  
          
          


  


        